                <h1>Q&amp;A: Jay Bilas discusses Duke’s 1982 recruiting class</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/d3ca09f8-5bdb-49b6-b8f1-67fa03b0576d.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="A&#x20;four-year&#x20;starter&#x20;at&#x20;Duke,&#x20;Jay&#x20;Bilas&#x20;is&#x20;now&#x20;a&#x20;college&#x20;basketball&#x20;analyst&#x20;for&#x20;ESPN." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            A four-year starter at Duke, Jay Bilas is now a college basketball analyst for ESPN.

